org.neo4j.graphdb

Interface Result.ResultRow

  • Enclosing interface:
    Result

    public static interface Result.ResultRow
    Describes a row of a result. The contents of this object is only stable during the visit call. The data it contains can change between calls to the visit method. Instances of this type should thus not be saved for later, or shared with other threads, rather the content should be copied.
